title: ubuntu budgie test 64 [Running] - Oracle VM VirtualBox_052.png
description:
We are pleased to announce our first beta release of #ubuntu budgie.

It has been an exciting few months ... and we expect lots more fun as we run up to 18.04 release date.

Have a quick read of what beta 1 UB is all about - our first LTS release - https://ubuntubudgie.org/blog/2018/03/08/18-04-release-notes
comments.comment:
